{
  "stem": "15577.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, at least myself, but I spoke afterwards with many, many friends of mine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, many of them have same reaction, the same feelings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If there was a selection, if something happened, and people were sent to death, or people was shot, or people were selected taken away, and we knew they won't come back, or we saw how they shot them-- never mind how-- what-- in what way they-- they killed them, the first feeling, or the first reaction wasn't, oh, how I am sorry.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even if-- if it was a-- somebody whom I was related with, or a very good friend of mine, or somebody who stood next to me or slept next to me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first feeling wasn't, oh, how sorry I am, how terrible it is he went.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first feeling was, how good it is I was left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was the big-- the victory of the Germans, in my opinion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Any of your family was part of a selection, during your time in Plaszow?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I told you, in Plaszow nobody was left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of us which were left-- ah!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once, my mother, my-- my-- ah, it was very dramatic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, I forget.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Once there was a very big selection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thousands were sent away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And among them was my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even at that moment, we saw them go away, from-- from very far, I don't remember that I was very, very moved.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember that I was crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember, or I remembered, that I was glad this was after the selection of the men.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't go together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the women were brought away.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
